🛠️  Supported HSMs:
   • SoftHSM2 (software)
   • Android StrongBox (mobile)
   • USB security token (FIDO2/CTAP2)
   • Solo 2 (FIDO2 token)
   • TPM (platform)
   • Any PKCS#11 device

🎯 Supported Algorithms:
   • AES-256-GCM
   • ChaCha20-Poly1305
   • Ed25519
   • RSA-4096
   • Genetic variants (adaptive)

💡 Quick Start:
   1. Discover HSMs: beardog hsm discover
   2. Collect entropy: beardog entropy collect --human-input --output seed.json
   3. Generate key: beardog key generate --key-id my-key --algorithm aes256-gcm
   4. Encrypt file: beardog encrypt --key my-key --input data.txt --output data.enc

